    { "@type": "Question", "name": "What are the highest-scoring CK words in Scrabble?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "JACKPOT (23 pts), QUICKLY (25 pts), HIJACK (22 pts), and KAYAK (15 pts with K reuse) are top scorers. CK words benefit from K's 5-point value making even short words like JACK (15 pts) very efficient." }},
