<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Words Containing CK — Scrabble Scoring Guide</h1>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">Published June 15, 2026 · 5 min read</p>

<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">CK is one of the most common ending patterns in English — BACK, KICK, LUCK, DECK. In Scrabble, the 8-point combined value of C and K makes these compact words surprisingly powerful, especially when you can slot them into tight board positions or hook them onto existing plays.</p>

<h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">CK by the Numbers</h2>

<div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
